title: Fruit cake with apples
ingredients: ['750g apples, peeled, cored and diced', '250g caster sugar', '250g sultanas', 'rum', '1 teaspoon cinnamon', '1 teaspoon ground cloves', '2 teaspoons mixed spice', '500g plain flour', '4 teaspoons baking powder', '200g nuts of your choice, coarsely chopped', '1 tablespoon unsweetened baking cocoa']
